1
00:00:46,413 --> 00:00:47,413
Kim!

2
00:00:49,149 --> 00:00:50,749
..have we ever met each other?

3
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:52,885
Why...

4
00:00:52,886 --> 00:00:54,721
do I draw your portrait.

5
00:00:55,211 --> 00:00:56,455
You remember me?

6
00:00:56,456 --> 00:00:59,067
These days, Tao Sor seems to want to remember things a lot more.

7
00:00:59,474 --> 00:01:02,844
Tao Sor remembering isn't an easy thing, you know?

8
00:01:04,431 --> 00:01:08,334
This picture... is the first one you drew.

9
00:01:09,602 --> 00:01:12,604
I don't have to introduce myself, right?

10
00:01:12,605 --> 00:01:14,606
Everyone remembers me...

11
00:01:14,607 --> 00:01:16,276
but I can't remember anyone.

12
00:01:16,910 --> 00:01:21,547
He has to be exposed to the same situation for a good length of time

13
00:01:21,548 --> 00:01:24,550
I'm Bruce. Nice to meet you.

14
00:01:25,117 --> 00:01:27,553
I'm Peter.

15
00:01:27,767 --> 00:01:29,164
And what about people?

16
00:01:29,266 --> 00:01:32,268
This... I'm not so sure about.

17
00:01:32,425 --> 00:01:34,201
He just brought some people to learn cooking.

18
00:01:35,453 --> 00:01:36,996
You don't know each other.

19
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:07,693
I think...

20
00:02:07,694 --> 00:02:09,762
I should leave.

21
00:02:20,173 --> 00:02:22,908
Hey, you!

22
00:02:22,909 --> 00:02:24,210
Where are you running off to?

23
00:03:38,318 --> 00:03:41,321
Startled?

24
00:03:43,723 --> 00:03:47,593
Why would you...

25
00:03:47,594 --> 00:03:49,028
do that to me?

26
00:03:51,056 --> 00:03:52,509
I'm just...

27
00:03:53,939 --> 00:03:55,874
doing what I feel like doing.

28
00:03:58,630 --> 00:04:00,272
I'm the one...

29
00:04:00,506 --> 00:04:02,741
that'll be your memory.

30
00:06:21,490 --> 00:06:22,456
Chef Mochi..

31
00:06:24,610 --> 00:06:26,463
Why do you look so out of it tomay?

32
00:06:26,488 --> 00:06:29,491
Wait! Out of it today?

33
00:06:32,351 --> 00:06:34,353
Do I really look like that?

34
00:06:34,833 --> 00:06:36,902
I dunno, I'm just playing around!

35
00:06:37,305 --> 00:06:39,879
You're worried about teaching today, right?

36
00:06:42,308 --> 00:06:45,211
It's not that..
- Huh? Then what is it?

37
00:06:49,296 --> 00:06:51,085
I'm not sure either.

38
00:06:51,565 --> 00:06:53,245
Hmm...

39
00:06:53,532 --> 00:06:55,013
Don't be worried, Chef Mochi.

40
00:06:55,258 --> 00:06:58,185
This isn't your first time, you'll figure it out.

41
00:06:59,138 --> 00:07:02,120
But either way, just prep your station for the time being.

42
00:07:02,254 --> 00:07:04,198
Looks like there's a few things missing

43
00:07:04,736 --> 00:07:07,239
I'll go get the rest.

44
00:07:24,076 --> 00:07:25,076
Tao Sor!

45
00:07:31,384 --> 00:07:33,552
What are we going to make today, Chef?

46
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:35,754
Pom Poms for sure!

47
00:07:35,902 --> 00:07:38,571
What you mean, pom poms? It's Wontons!

48
00:07:39,718 --> 00:07:43,789
I've brought these two to learn with you before, Mangmo and Future.

49
00:07:45,598 --> 00:07:47,967
The clip we posted last time got a ton of hits!

50
00:07:49,168 --> 00:07:50,836
Hey, the view over there's nice!

51
00:07:50,837 --> 00:07:52,771
Should we go take some inserts?

52
00:07:52,772 --> 00:07:54,307
Alright!
- Let's go!

53
00:08:02,114 --> 00:08:03,815
I'm Kim.

54
00:08:04,248 --> 00:08:07,218
Do you need me to help with anything?

55
00:08:11,735 --> 00:08:13,003
Have we ever met before?

56
00:08:14,991 --> 00:08:17,726
We made a promise to each other.

57
00:08:17,751 --> 00:08:19,453
Do you remember anything?

58
00:08:23,736 --> 00:08:25,471
Promise?

59
00:08:26,372 --> 00:08:27,707
When?

60
00:08:28,907 --> 00:08:30,463
Yesterday!

61
00:08:31,270 --> 00:08:32,760
I promised you...

62
00:08:33,812 --> 00:08:35,693
that I would be your memory.

63
00:08:38,884 --> 00:08:43,155
I'm the one that will be your memory.

64
00:09:00,573 --> 00:09:03,376
Why...

65
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:07,713
did you say exactly what I heard in my dreams?

66
00:09:09,749 --> 00:09:11,517
Sometimes...

67
00:09:13,638 --> 00:09:16,541
these things aren't just from your dreams.

68
00:09:20,156 --> 00:09:20,792
I...

69
00:09:21,083 --> 00:09:22,961
am your yesterday.

70
00:09:22,962 --> 00:09:26,064
The two of us...

71
00:09:26,065 --> 00:09:27,433
kissed.

72
00:09:37,209 --> 00:09:38,343
Oh!

73
00:09:38,344 --> 00:09:39,644
Our students have arrived!

74
00:09:39,645 --> 00:09:41,647
Shall we get started, Chef Mochi?

75
00:09:45,251 --> 00:09:46,852
OK

76
00:10:30,229 --> 00:10:32,732
Nice view, don't you think?

77
00:10:35,777 --> 00:10:36,777
Sure.

78
00:10:38,513 --> 00:10:40,482
It is a nice view, but..

79
00:10:40,992 --> 00:10:44,652
I think, if it was renovated to look more modern...

80
00:10:45,652 --> 00:10:50,824
you could bring in more tourists, for example young folks and so newer.

81
00:10:53,829 --> 00:10:55,897
I like the same old things

82
00:10:55,898 --> 00:10:57,733
not a fan of change.

83
00:10:59,234 --> 00:11:01,403
The Treasure Resort is like this

84
00:11:02,170 --> 00:11:03,805
and that's how people remember it

85
00:11:05,679 --> 00:11:06,914
if..

86
00:11:07,409 --> 00:11:08,710
Then...

87
00:11:09,878 --> 00:11:12,881
if there's nothing, I'll excuse myself

88
00:11:13,248 --> 00:11:14,683
I think you...

89
00:11:16,539 --> 00:11:18,841
should go do your job properly.

90
00:11:20,076 --> 00:11:23,546
Although I know how you feel about Tao Sor

91
00:11:23,991 --> 00:11:26,994
I'll have to warn you a second time.

92
00:11:27,929 --> 00:11:29,464
Quit messing with Tao Sor's life.

93
00:11:31,298 --> 00:11:34,902
This situation is far more delicate and complicated than you think.

94
00:12:06,468 --> 00:12:13,875
Hello, we're from Siam Sea. Could we invite you to come promote our yachts?

95
00:12:16,244 --> 00:12:19,247
Doesn't look professional at all...

96
00:12:28,957 --> 00:12:37,271
To Miss Nao. I - a representative of Siam Sea, am inviting you to be a part of our yacht business promotional campaign.

97
00:12:37,341 --> 00:12:41,345
If you have any interest, we are happy to provide more details.

98
00:12:42,237 --> 00:12:45,240
Now I look like a scammer.

99
00:13:12,067 --> 00:13:13,869
Just send it!

100
00:13:23,655 --> 00:13:30,795
I'm interested. When? Tomorrow?

101
00:13:36,901 --> 00:13:39,603
We can do tomorrow. Please give me a copy of your ID, I will get you a ticket.

102
00:13:39,604 --> 00:13:42,607
Are you for real?

103
00:13:50,048 --> 00:13:53,051
Too fast?

104
00:13:54,919 --> 00:13:55,654
We could do some other day.

105
00:13:55,655 --> 00:13:58,657
We could do some other day.
- No, tomorrow's fine.

106
00:14:06,631 --> 00:14:08,600
Hm? You don't have class today?

107
00:14:11,435 --> 00:14:16,713
Sis, I got an influencer to come shoot content for us. See? What do you think.

108
00:14:22,236 --> 00:14:23,847
Don't spend too much!

109
00:14:24,257 --> 00:14:27,460
It's gonna be monsoon season soon, can't do much for sales.

110
00:14:27,730 --> 00:14:29,731
Sis, just wait and see.

111
00:14:29,732 --> 00:14:31,299
This will be a new thing.

112
00:14:31,300 --> 00:14:35,436
If a famous fortune teller does readings on our boats,

113
00:14:35,437 --> 00:14:37,538
Our boats are gonna get huge!

114
00:14:37,539 --> 00:14:40,541
People will hoard to us, right?

115
00:14:40,542 --> 00:14:43,811
Feeling like they're absorbing energy from nature itself.

116
00:14:43,812 --> 00:14:45,813
Alright, whatever.

117
00:14:45,814 --> 00:14:47,615
But when are they coming?

118
00:14:47,616 --> 00:14:48,117
Tomorrow!

119
00:14:48,183 --> 00:14:49,599
Tomorrow...

120
00:14:49,624 --> 00:14:50,926
Tomorrow?!!

121
00:14:51,209 --> 00:14:52,476
You crazy?

122
00:14:52,677 --> 00:14:53,945
You just told me!

123
00:14:55,124 --> 00:14:56,425
What are you doing?

124
00:14:57,893 --> 00:15:02,731
Didn't you say so yourself? Monsoon season's coming, people aren't gonna come.

125
00:15:04,654 --> 00:15:06,455
Alright, alright!

126
00:15:06,557 --> 00:15:09,560
Just don't use the bigger ones, it's a waste of fuel.

127
00:15:10,839 --> 00:15:14,240
Ok... Dad. I'm outta here!

128
00:15:14,265 --> 00:15:17,268
And where are you off to now?
- Central!

129
00:15:42,404 --> 00:15:45,238
About what you said yesterday, that we...

130
00:15:45,263 --> 00:15:46,364
Kissed?

131
00:15:48,110 --> 00:15:49,477
Did we really kiss?

132
00:15:49,502 --> 00:15:52,938
Then that means that we're a couple, right?

133
00:15:52,963 --> 00:15:54,363
And, and..

134
00:15:54,388 --> 00:15:55,955
Does Talay know about this?

135
00:15:55,984 --> 00:16:00,089
I don't think he does. Because if he did, he would've told me...

136
00:16:01,934 --> 00:16:03,803
Who exactly are you?

137
00:16:04,660 --> 00:16:06,328
I already told you

138
00:16:06,906 --> 00:16:08,708
that I'll be your memory for you.

139
00:16:10,221 --> 00:16:13,691
Prove it! A picture or something that says we're a couple.

140
00:16:15,269 --> 00:16:17,603
So, the thing is...

141
00:16:17,628 --> 00:16:21,532
we're not exactly at that point yet, but..

142
00:16:36,825 --> 00:16:40,294
Or if you still don't believe me,

143
00:16:40,295 --> 00:16:41,930
should we try this?

144
00:17:15,464 --> 00:17:17,099
Tao Sor!

145
00:17:20,435 --> 00:17:21,904
Excuse me...

146
00:17:59,007 --> 00:17:59,912
Hello?

147
00:18:00,025 --> 00:18:02,594
Is that... a picture I drew?

148
00:18:02,899 --> 00:18:03,734
Of course!

149
00:18:03,759 --> 00:18:07,762
You were drawing me on the beach while I was surfing

150
00:18:08,718 --> 00:18:10,352
and I saw you.

151
00:18:10,408 --> 00:18:12,609
So I walked straight up to you.

152
00:18:12,634 --> 00:18:15,637
From there, we talked a little

153
00:18:16,402 --> 00:18:18,603
and you gave me this picture.

154
00:18:18,737 --> 00:18:20,906
You signed your name on the top corner as well.

155
00:18:22,019 --> 00:18:25,022
After that, I invited you to come surf with me.

156
00:18:25,945 --> 00:18:28,881
But you were afraid of the ocean.

157
00:18:29,193 --> 00:18:31,228
You know that much about me?

158
00:18:31,461 --> 00:18:32,601
Then...

159
00:18:32,762 --> 00:18:35,697
how did we end up kissing?

160
00:18:35,899 --> 00:18:37,890
Well, yesterday...

161
00:18:38,935 --> 00:18:42,706
we went to an aquarium together.

162
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:46,943
After that, we just walked around for a bit

163
00:18:47,089 --> 00:18:48,427
after that...

164
00:18:48,452 --> 00:18:51,955
the atmosphere just led me to...

165
00:18:52,883 --> 00:18:54,218
kiss you.

166
00:18:55,186 --> 00:18:57,276
I have to apologize for that, Tao Sor.

167
00:18:57,490 --> 00:19:00,492
For... not asking for your consent.

168
00:19:00,517 --> 00:19:01,752
Forget it.

169
00:19:02,838 --> 00:19:05,139
I...

170
00:19:05,164 --> 00:19:06,832
wouldn't remember anyway.

171
00:19:09,257 --> 00:19:10,558
That's all.
- Oh!

172
00:19:11,158 --> 00:19:12,493
Hold on a moment, Tao Sor.

173
00:19:13,950 --> 00:19:15,485
In that case...

174
00:19:16,953 --> 00:19:20,589
let's get to know each other better

175
00:19:20,590 --> 00:19:21,791
could we?

176
00:19:23,347 --> 00:19:24,882
My name is Tao Sor.

177
00:19:27,964 --> 00:19:29,766
I like cooking.

178
00:19:31,201 --> 00:19:32,802
I'm afraid of the ocean.

179
00:19:35,238 --> 00:19:36,505
As for me,

180
00:19:36,506 --> 00:19:37,874
my name is Kim

181
00:19:38,208 --> 00:19:39,708
I'm from Bangkok

182
00:19:39,709 --> 00:19:42,044
I had to come to my hometown of Phuket

183
00:19:42,045 --> 00:19:43,846
for a period of 1 year.

184
00:19:43,847 --> 00:19:48,885
Because my mother was told by a Feng Shui master that I have to fix my year of bad fortune here.

185
00:19:49,385 --> 00:19:53,690
And... when you surf, how does it feel?

186
00:19:54,724 --> 00:19:57,025
It makes me feel like...

187
00:19:57,026 --> 00:20:00,562
I fall nto a world with no noise

188
00:20:00,563 --> 00:20:02,364
no people,

189
00:20:02,365 --> 00:20:03,866
nothing at all...

190
00:20:03,867 --> 00:20:06,870
except the waves that hit my body.

191
00:20:09,239 --> 00:20:11,708
Really? What else is there?

192
00:20:12,642 --> 00:20:14,444
The water hits us,

193
00:20:14,878 --> 00:20:17,881
But we have to understand the timing.

194
00:20:18,715 --> 00:20:21,517
Kind of like trying to speak to it.

195
00:20:21,518 --> 00:20:23,185
The stronger the waves,

196
00:20:23,186 --> 00:20:26,189
the more fun it is, making me feel even more alive.

197
00:20:26,923 --> 00:20:28,891
It's like flying, Tao Sor.

198
00:20:28,892 --> 00:20:32,361
It's.. not just a sport.

199
00:20:32,362 --> 00:20:33,563
But...

200
00:20:33,863 --> 00:20:35,465
It's like freedom.

201
00:20:36,132 --> 00:20:40,002
We just have to go with the flow and that's enough.

202
00:20:40,003 --> 00:20:41,503
Thank you.

203
00:20:41,504 --> 00:20:44,873
If you really are my memory.

204
00:20:44,874 --> 00:20:47,242
Could you help writing down

205
00:20:47,243 --> 00:20:49,646
that I want to try doing it once.

206
00:20:52,148 --> 00:20:53,583
Thank you as well.

207
00:20:54,918 --> 00:20:56,618
I hope...

208
00:20:56,619 --> 00:20:59,154
you'll be able to remember me, Tao Sor.

209
00:20:59,155 --> 00:21:03,660
Sweet dreams, Kim. I hope I'll be able to remeber you tomorrow.

210
00:21:04,394 --> 00:21:07,029
Sweet dreams. Have a good night.

211
00:21:07,030 --> 00:21:08,932
Thank you, Kim.

212
00:21:20,410 --> 00:21:22,912
You better remember me, Tao Sor!

213
00:21:42,643 --> 00:21:46,914
Hello? Where are you? I'm waiting at the parking lot.

214
00:21:49,083 --> 00:21:53,453
I'm actually getting coffee, please wait a moment.

215
00:21:53,554 --> 00:21:56,891
Should I go to you?
- Nao!

216
00:22:06,022 --> 00:22:08,291
I'm over here!

217
00:22:26,042 --> 00:22:29,946
I'm sorry, I didn't remember that you were SilvyStar.

218
00:22:30,113 --> 00:22:33,448
You know my channel too?

219
00:22:33,449 --> 00:22:35,985
Probably a lot more than you think I do.

220
00:22:37,920 --> 00:22:41,357
Shall we get going?

221
00:22:44,394 --> 00:22:45,995
Okay.

222
00:22:48,031 --> 00:22:49,198
Shall we go?

223
00:23:08,184 --> 00:23:13,989
Happy holidays, everyone! Today I'm aboard a luxurious boat from Siam Sea, in order to take in some fresh, natural energy!

224
00:23:13,990 --> 00:23:21,197
It's said that celebs and idols like travelling to different places to absorb different energies.

225
00:23:25,668 --> 00:23:28,103
"Nao is so pretty.."

226
00:23:28,104 --> 00:23:32,642
Thank you so much, Aod! Don't forget to find time to take in some postive energy like this!

227
00:23:36,245 --> 00:23:38,947
"I want to get my fortune told too!"

228
00:23:38,948 --> 00:23:42,851
I'm in Phuket at the moment. If you could fly over here, I'll be glad to make an appointment!

229
00:23:42,852 --> 00:23:47,823
Alright, we're reached an important section of our time here, after absorbing some positive energy.

230
00:23:47,824 --> 00:23:50,827
Let's see just how accurate we can get.

231
00:23:51,861 --> 00:23:54,063
Does anyone want to try?

232
00:24:03,940 --> 00:24:05,742
Go on!

233
00:24:53,723 --> 00:24:57,360
Are my cards really that bad?

234
00:24:58,461 --> 00:25:03,698
Honestly, yes. They're not very good, both your career and love life.

235
00:25:03,699 --> 00:25:06,802
Looks like you won't reach your goals..

236
00:25:06,803 --> 00:25:11,674
What you desire, you might not get. What you don't, you wouldn't get anyways.

237
00:25:12,909 --> 00:25:19,248
But..it's okay! Since we're on a boat absorbing some good manna, it'll get better soon!

238
00:25:24,887 --> 00:25:28,423
In that case, do you want to continue your stream?

239
00:25:28,424 --> 00:25:30,704
In that case, do you want to continue your stream?
- Okay!

240
00:25:56,385 --> 00:25:58,820
Oh, I'm sorry!
- Be careful, it's hot!

241
00:25:58,821 --> 00:26:01,590
I got this for you.
- Thank you!

242
00:26:01,591 --> 00:26:03,726
Be careful, it's really hot!
- Okay.

243
00:26:03,759 --> 00:26:06,661
Are you taking photos? I can take them for you.
- Yes!

244
00:26:06,662 --> 00:26:08,030
That'll be great, thank you!

245
00:26:15,104 --> 00:26:18,841
Here! I wanna get this angle here.
- Oh, okay.

246
00:26:29,174 --> 00:26:30,308
Gorgeous!

247
00:27:01,551 --> 00:27:05,187
You wanna take one together?
- Hm? Together?
- Yes.

248
00:27:05,288 --> 00:27:07,389
How should we...
- I'll do it.

249
00:27:07,390 --> 00:27:08,724
Which spot's good? Over here?

250
00:27:13,017 --> 00:27:14,652
1, 2, 3!

251
00:29:33,402 --> 00:29:37,072
Someone asked what we'll do after we're done?

252
00:29:37,073 --> 00:29:40,508
I wanna visit so many places because I've never been here, but...

253
00:29:40,509 --> 00:29:42,611
I'm still not sure where to go.

254
00:30:19,804 --> 00:30:22,507
Oh, there's only a few photos?

255
00:30:23,296 --> 00:30:28,734
Oh. Sorry, Nao. My hands were shaking alot,
so I couldn't take a lot.

256
00:30:28,824 --> 00:30:30,859
Want some more? I'll take them for you.

257
00:30:30,860 --> 00:30:31,961
It's okay.

258
00:30:33,829 --> 00:30:38,768
Yeah, why did you have me come promote your family's business?

259
00:30:40,603 --> 00:30:41,737
Because...

260
00:30:44,006 --> 00:30:45,908
Because I like you.

261
00:30:47,009 --> 00:30:49,745
Are my cards really that bad?

262
00:30:51,647 --> 00:30:56,351
Honestly, yes. They're not very good, both your career and love life.

263
00:30:56,352 --> 00:31:01,490
Looks like you won't reach your goals..

264
00:31:01,791 --> 00:31:04,911
What you desire, you might not get. What you don't, you wouldn't get anyways.

265
00:31:08,964 --> 00:31:12,767
Actually, you seem to be pretty famous

266
00:31:12,768 --> 00:31:15,737
and it could bring in a lot of clients

267
